        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Second Amendment Guarantee Act or the SAGA Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits a state or local government from establishing a regulation, prohibition, or registration or licensing requirement with respect to a rifle or shotgun that is more restrictive (or that imposes a greater penalty) than federal law.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
